== Overview ==
The Security Countermand is a [[:Category:Modules (Utility)|non combat module]] that can be used to override electronic security devices. It is a favorite amongst thieves and special forces.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Security Countermand can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
